FIRST NAT. BANK OF BATH, Respondent, v. ROBY, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by the First National Bank of Bath against Sidney B. Roby.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Order appealed from affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
